</strong></em></p>\n<p>So require&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a = b\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>b</mi>\n</math></span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>M1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[4 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"11841","referenceCode":"EXM.1.AHL.TZ0.16a","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Find a relationship between a and b if the matrices M = ( 1 a 2 3 ) and N = ( 1 b 2 3 ) commute under matrix multiplication.","paper":"1","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 4]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","AHL 1.14—Introduction to matrices"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}